column4: RPT-Elon Musk's 'Teslaquila' drink faces clash with Mexican tequila industry
column5: MEXICO CITY  Nov 13 Tesla Inc co-founder Elon Musk and Mexico's tequila producers could be headed for a collision after the agave-based drink's industry group opposed the flamboyant billionaire's efforts to trademark an alcoholic drink dubbed "Teslaquila."
